izing: border-box; width: 1160px; display: flex;"><div data-id="b12e115" data-element_type="column" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; min-height: 1px; display: flex; width: 1160px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1160px; position: relative; display: flex; padding: 0px 10px 10px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; width: 1140px; flex-wrap: wrap; align-content: flex-start; display: flex;"><div data-id="7c752be" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; width: 1140px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: background 0.3s ease 0s, border 0.3s ease 0s, border-radius 0.3s ease 0s, box-shadow 0.3s ease 0s, -webkit-border-radius 0.3s ease 0s, -webkit-box-shadow 0.3s ease 0s;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">Prognozlashtirish va makroiqtisodiy tadqiqotlar instituti (PMTI) ish haqining ta&rsquo;lim darajasiga bog&lsquo;liq holda ortib borishini o&lsquo;rganib chiqdi.</em></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Yuqori va past malakali ish o&lsquo;rinlarida mehnatga to&lsquo;lanadigan &nbsp;ish haqi o&lsquo;rtasidagi tafovut bilan birga, xodimlar malakasi, ko&lsquo;nikmasi hamda eng past ta&rsquo;lim darajasiga qo&lsquo;yiladigan talablar ham ortib bormoqda. Xodimlarning malaka darajasiga qo&lsquo;yiladigan talablarning muttasil ortib borishi, o&lsquo;z navbatida butun dunyoda &quot;umr bo&lsquo;yi ta&rsquo;lim&quot; konsepsiyasini yanada ommalashtirmoqda. O&lsquo;zbekistonda ta&rsquo;limning nisbatan yuqoriroq darajasidagi diplom egalari mehnat bozori ishtirokchisiga aylangach, sarflagan vaqti va kuchini oqlaydigan kompensatsiya olayaptimi? Ushbu savollarga ilmiy asoslangan javoblarni olish uchun PMTI ekspertlari rasmiy ta&rsquo;lim darajalarining ish haqiga ta&rsquo;sirini, iqtisodiyot sohalari va ta&rsquo;lim darajalari bo&lsquo;yicha empirik baholashga qaratilgan tadqiqot o&lsquo;tkazdi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Tadqiqot natijalariga ko&lsquo;ra, O&lsquo;zbekistonda ish haqidagi ustama fan doktori (yoki&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">DSc</strong>) ilmiy unvoni uchun&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">61% dan</strong>,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">PhD</strong> yoki fan nomzodi uchun&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">41% dan</strong> yuqori ekanligi, shu bilan birga bakalavr bosqichining imtiyozli diplomiga ega xodimlar mehnat bozorida oddiy diplom sohiblariga qaraganda 8,5% ko&lsquo;proq maosh olishi aniqlandi.&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Ushbu tadqiqot yuqori ta&rsquo;lim darajasiga ega bo&lsquo;lish uchun sarflangan vaqt va kuch o&lsquo;zini oqlanishini tasdiqladi.</strong></h3><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(114, 114, 114); text-align: center;"><img height="904" src="https://imrs.uz/public/ckfinder/userfiles/files/uz.jpg" width="1280" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: none; height: auto; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 0px; box-shadow: none;" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">O&lsquo;zbekistonda ta&rsquo;limning yuqoriroq bosqichlari keltiradigan iqtisodiy manfaatni baholash uchun PMTI mutaxassislari&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">18 yoshdan katta fuqarolar</strong> ishtirokida&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&ldquo;Ta&rsquo;limning daromadga ta&rsquo;siri&rdquo;</strong> mavzusida onlayn so&lsquo;rov o&lsquo;tkazdi. Unda asosan ijtimoiy tarmoqlardan faol foydalanuvchi tasodifiy respondentlar qatnashdi.&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Mamlakatimizning turli hududlaridan onlayn tartibida jami 1152 ta (61% erkaklar, 39% ayollardan) javob olindi.&nbsp;</strong>Tadqiqotda 906 ta so&lsquo;rovnomaning natijasi baholandi (o&lsquo;z hohishiga ko&lsquo;ra ishlamaydigan, vaqtincha ishsiz, farzand tarbiyasi bilan band, kunduzgi bakalavriat, magistratura, tayanch doktorantura va doktoranturada ta&rsquo;lim oluvchi fuqarolarning javoblari, shuningdek, noto&lsquo;g&lsquo;ri to&lsquo;ldirilgan hamda bir xil javoblar inobatga olinmadi).</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Ta&rsquo;lim darajasi bo&lsquo;yicha 906 nafar respondentning 3,3% ini DSc (yoki fan doktorlari), 18,2% ini PhD (yoki fan nomzodlari), 33,1% ini magistrlar, 33,3% ini bakalavrlar, 15,3% ini bakalavriat va magistratura tizimi tatbiq etilgunga qadar oliy ta&rsquo;lim olganlar, 7,0% ini o&lsquo;rta maxsus, professional ta&rsquo;lim muassasalarining bitiruvchilari, 3,0% ini o&lsquo;rta va 0,4% ini tayanch o&lsquo;rta (9 sinf) bilimga ega bo&lsquo;lganlar tashkil etdi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Ta&rsquo;limning iqtisodiy manfaati ko&lsquo;pchilikka yaxshi tanish bo&lsquo;lgan&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&ldquo;Minserning daromadlar tenglamasi</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&rdquo;</strong> (birinchisi &ndash; ta&rsquo;lim davomiyligi uchun, ikkinchisi &ndash; ta&rsquo;lim darajalari uchun) asosida tahlil qilindi:</h3><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(114, 114, 114);">&nbsp;</p><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">Ln</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">W</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">i</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">=</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">a</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">0</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">+</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">&alpha;G</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">i</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">+r</em>S<em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">i</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">+</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">&beta;</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">i</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">ex</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">p</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">i</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">+</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">&beta;</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">i</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">ex</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">p</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">i</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">2</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">+</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">&epsilon;i &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</em>(1)</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Bu yerda: W &ndash; ish haqining miqdori;&nbsp;<em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">G</em> &ndash; jins;&nbsp;<em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">S</em> &ndash; ta&rsquo;lim yillari; exp &ndash; potensial tajriba; &epsilon; &ndash; tasodifiy xatolik. r &ndash; koeffitsiyenti ta&rsquo;limning iqtisodiy manfaatini o&lsquo;lchaydi va individlarning ta&rsquo;lim olish muddati bir yilga oshganda o&lsquo;rtacha ish haqi necha foizga oshishini ko&lsquo;rsatadi&raquo; . &alpha; &ndash; tanlangan jins uchun ta&rsquo;limning iqtisodiy manfaati; &beta; &ndash; potensial ish tajribasining iqtisodiy manfaat koeffitsiyenti.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Tenglamaning ikkinchi ko&lsquo;rinishida ta&rsquo;lim yillari ta&rsquo;lim darajalari bilan almashtiriladi.<br style="box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">Ln</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">W</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">i</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">=</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">a</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">0</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">+</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">&alpha;G</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">i</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">+</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">p</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">1</em>L<em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">1i</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">+&hellip;+</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">p</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">1</em>L<em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">Ni</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">+</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">&beta;</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">1</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">ex</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">p</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">i</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">+</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">&beta;</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">2</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">ex</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">p</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">i</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">2</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">+</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">&epsilon;i &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</em>(2)</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Bu yerda:&nbsp;<em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">L1, &hellip;, LN</em>&nbsp; &ndash; ta&rsquo;lim darajasi N &nbsp;uchun kiritilgan 1 va 0 qiymatini oluvchi ko&lsquo;rsatkichlar. Ularning oldidagi &rho; - koeffitsiyenti ta&rsquo;lim darajalari uchun iqtisodiy manfaatni baholaydi va u yoki bu ta&rsquo;lim darajasiga ega xodimlarning ish haqi referent guruh ishchilarning maoshiga nisbatan necha foizga ortiqligini ko&lsquo;rsatadi&raquo; .</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Ikkala tenglamada ham potensial ish tajribasi ko&lsquo;rsatkichi tushirib qoldirildi . Ta&rsquo;lim darajalari sifatida&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">DSc&nbsp;</strong>(Doctor of science) yoki fan doktori hamda&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">PhD (</strong>Doctor of Philosophy) yoki fan nomzodi ilmiy darajalari tanlandi. Baholash&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Stata dasturiy ta&rsquo;minotida</strong> eng kichik kvadratlar uslubida amalga oshirildi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Baholash natijalariga ko&lsquo;ra (1-jadval) O&lsquo;zbekistonda har bir qo&lsquo;shimcha ta&rsquo;lim yili ish haqining o&lsquo;rtacha&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">10% oshishiga</strong> imkoniyat yaratadi va bu ko&lsquo;rsatkich BMTning ta&rsquo;lim, fan va madaniyat masalalari bo&lsquo;yicha tashkiloti - YUNЕSKO ning bahosiga mos keladi:&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&laquo;Butun dunyo bo&lsquo;yicha, 139 ta davlatda daromadlilik me&rsquo;yori ta&rsquo;limning har bir qo&lsquo;shimcha yiliga 10% ni tashkil qiladi&raquo;</strong>.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">DSc yoki fan doktori ilmiy unvoniga ega va iqtisodiyotda band bo&lsquo;lganlar o&lsquo;rta hisobda 61%, PhD yoki fan nomzodlari esa o&lsquo;zlaridan oldingi ta&rsquo;lim darajasiga ega xodimlarga nisbatan 41% ko&lsquo;proq maosh oladi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Imtiyozli diplomga ega respondentlar</strong> (bakalavr bosqichi bitiruvchilari yoki Bolon tizimiga o&lsquo;tilgunga qadar OTMlarning bitiruvchilari) mehnat bozorida oddiy diplom sohiblariga nisbatan&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">8,5% ko&lsquo;proq maosh oladi.</strong></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">So&lsquo;rovda ishtirok etganlar orasida iqtisodiyot tarmoqlari bo&lsquo;yicha kompyuter texnologiyalari sohasida band bo&lsquo;lganlarning o&lsquo;rtacha oylik maoshi eng yuqori ekanligi ma&rsquo;lum bo&lsquo;ldi. Ular (ta&rsquo;lim darajasi va uning davomiyligiga qarab) boshqa tarmoqlarda band bo&lsquo;lganlarga nisbatan 28% dan 37% gacha ko&lsquo;proq ish haqi oladi. Iqtisodchilar 24-37%, moliyachilar 29-30%, professional va ilmiy-texnik faoliyat (yuridik, konsalting, buxgalteriya va professional xizmatlar) bilan shug&lsquo;ullanuvchilarning o&lsquo;rtacha oylik maoshi 27-38% ko&lsquo;p ekanligi oydinlashdi. Davlat boshqaruvi va mudofaa yo&lsquo;nalishlarida band bo&lsquo;lganlar o&lsquo;z mehnati evaziga 25-31% ko&lsquo;proq maosh oladi. Sanoat tarmog&lsquo;i vakillari 22-24%, qurilish sohasi vakillari esa 25% ko&lsquo;p ish haqi olishi aniqlandi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Umuman, iqtisodiyotda erkaklarning maoshi ayollarnikiga nisbatan 23% dan 28% gacha yuqori. Shu bilan birga har bir qo&lsquo;shimcha ta&rsquo;lim yili ayollarning daromadini 11% ga, erkaklarnikini 8,7% ga oshiradi. Oilali erkaklar bo&lsquo;ydoqlarga nisbatan 16% ko&lsquo;proq maosh olsa, turmush qurganidan so&lsquo;ng ayollarning maoshi 27% ga kamayishi kuzatiladi. Poytaxtimiz mehnat bozorida band bo&lsquo;lganlarning ish haqi boshqa hududlardagi ish haqiga nisbatan 23-24% (erkaklarda 30%, ayollarda 16,3%) yuqoriroq.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Ta&rsquo;lim darajasi turlicha bo&lsquo;lgan respondentlarning oylik maoshi o&lsquo;rtasidagi tafovut tahsil olayotganlar va ularning oilalariga oila a&rsquo;zosining ta&rsquo;lim olishi uchun sarmoya kiritish bo&lsquo;yicha to&lsquo;g&lsquo;ri qaror qabul qilishda yordam beradi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">PMTI ekspertlari tadqiqotning keyingi bosqichida zarur bilim, mahorat va yuqori malakaga ega bo&lsquo;lib, ma&rsquo;lum bir kasbni egallash uchun qancha miqdorda sarmoya kiritish zarurligini hisoblash imkonini beradigan kalkulyatorni ishlab chiqishni rejalashtirmoqda.</em></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: right;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">1-</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">jadval.</strong></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">O&lsquo;zbekistonda ta&rsquo;lim daraja</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">si</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">ning ish haqiga ta&rsquo;siri</strong></h3><table cellspacing="0" style="box-sizing: border-box; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; width: 624px;"><tbody style="box-sizing: border-box;"><tr style="box-sizing: border-box;"><td rowspan="2" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black; background-color: rgb(226, 239, 217); height: 26px; width: 148px;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Ko&lsquo;rsatkichlarning nomlanishi</strong></h3></td><td colspan="2" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px; border-top: 1px solid black; border-right: 1px solid black; border-bottom: 1px solid black; border-left: none; border-image: initial; background-color: rgb(226, 239, 217); height: 26px; width: 237px;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 40